OL,3,CTeenager 'lost leg' in alleged hit-and-
OL,4,Crun
OL,6,FA fundraiser has been started in aid
OL,7,Fof a boy who reportedly lost a leg
OL,8,Fafter he was hit by a car which then
OL,9,Ffled the scene.
OL,11,FThe 17-year-old was on Halifax Road,
OL,12,FBradford, when he was knocked down on
OL,13,FMonday, 16 September.
OL,15,FHe was taken to Leeds General
OL,16,FInfirmary, where he remains in a
OL,17,Fcritical condition.
OL,19,FAn online fundraiser has received
OL,20,Falmost #10,000 in donations.
