OL,3,CTeenager 'lost leg' in alleged hit-and-
OL,4,Crun
OL,6,FOrganiser Michaela Petty said the
OL,7,Fteenager had been to the local Tesco
OL,8,Fstore and was crossing the road when
OL,9,Fhe was hit.
OL,11,FShe said: "(He) is still in hospital
OL,12,Fin a coma, still in a critical
OL,13,Fcondition due to his injuries.
OL,15,F"He's been in theatre twice for major,
OL,16,Flife-changing operations which one led
OL,17,Fto him having to have his leg off up
OL,18,Fto his thigh."
