OL,6,FThe boy faces the prospect of several
OL,7,Fweeks in hospital and "it's going to
OL,8,Fbe one hell of a journey for his
OL,9,Ffamily and friends," she said.
OL,11,FThe money raised would support his
OL,12,Ffamily and aid his recovery.
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police said the
OL,15,Fincident happened after officers in a
OL,16,Fmarked car saw a car driving at speed
OL,17,Fon the opposite carriageway on Halifax
OL,18,FRoad at about 8.25pm.
