OL,6,FThey turned around to pursue the car
OL,7,Fbut lost sight of it, before finding
OL,8,Fthe 17-year-old at the scene.
OL,10,FThree men have been arrested over the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FA 33-year-old men and a 24-year-old
OL,14,Fman have been arrested on suspicion of
OL,15,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving.
OL,18,FA third man, aged 33, was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
